ActOther Than Statutory Authority
SubjectAmendments to Annexes II, VIII and IX to the Basel Convention on the Control of Transboundary Movements of Hazardous Wastes and their Disposal
PrecisOrder authorizing the Minister of Foreign Affairs to take the actions necessary to ACCEPT, on behalf of Canada, the AMENDMENTS TO ANNEXES II, VIII AND IX TO THE BASEL CONVENTION ON THE CONTROL OF TRANSBOUNDARY MOVEMENTS OF HAZARDOUS WASTES AND THEIR DISPOSAL, adopted at Geneva on May 10, 2019.
